WEBVTT

00:01.929 --> 00:03.680
- Previously on Angel:
- That's her.

00:04.330 --> 00:07.950
So you're what they
brought back in that box as human.

00:08.529 --> 00:12.390
- We want him dark, not dead.
- Forces can change Angel to Angelus.

00:13.330 --> 00:15.429
He knows happiness, he goes evil.

00:15.730 --> 00:17.829
We were together 150 years.

00:18.730 --> 00:20.800
- The middle one.
- She has the sight.

00:21.129 --> 00:24.010
She is innocence.
We'll turn her into one of us.

00:24.730 --> 00:28.170
The gypsies gave you a soul.
A filthy soul! No!

00:29.530 --> 00:32.340
- I remember everything.
- You have a soul now.

00:32.530 --> 00:35.549
Soon those memories start
eating away at you.

00:36.729 --> 00:38.590
Believe me, I know.

00:40.000 --> 00:46.074
